u need to understand.<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p>Sometimes you may not understand all the topics in this plan either practices or tools and technologies, but try to continue and you will find by reaching out to the end of the plan, it will clear many of what you didn&#8217;t understand in the beginning.<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p>Also, I am planning to go live for free sessions for Q&amp;A to answer any question regarding any miss understanding parts and open the doors for complex parts as well as sharing the real experience regarding people&#8217;s questions.<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h3>Here are the links for the live session to register.<\/h3>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/bit.ly\/3c6nRYr\">https:\/\/bit.ly\/3c6nRYr<\/a><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h3>Here is the plan:<\/h3>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/mohamedradwan.com\/2020\/04\/08\/qa-live-session-for-how-to-become-a-devops-expert\/devops-expert\/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-10001\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-10001\" src=\"https:\/\/mohamedradwan.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/DevOps-Expert.jpg\" alt=\"DevOps Expert\" width=\"768\" height=\"413\" srcset=\"https:\/\/mohamedradwan.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/DevOps-Expert.jpg 768w, https:\/\/mohamedradwan.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/DevOps-Expert-300x161.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h3>Watch the following videos. Please respect the order.<\/h3>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/mohamedradwan.com\/2020\/04\/08\/qa-live-session-for-how-to-become-a-devops-expert\/devops-videos\/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-10014\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-10014\" src=\"https:\/\/mohamedradwan.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/DevOps-Videos.png\" alt=\"DevOps Videos\" width=\"790\" height=\"479\" srcset=\"https:\/\/mohamedradwan.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/DevOps-Videos.png 790w, https:\/\/mohamedra